  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTIONS 59-21-127 AND 59-23-5, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROHIBIT LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS OF THE MISSISSIPPI DEPARTMENT OF MARINE RESOURCES FROM BOARDING ANY VESSEL OR PERFORMING A VESSEL STOP UNLESS THE OFFICER HAS PROBABLE CAUSE TO BELIEVE THAT A VIOLATION OF THE BOATING SAFETY LAW HAS OCCURRED OR IS OCCURRING; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
